    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden New Jersey U S America<ptr target="bms.00004_n1"
                        /></name>
                    <date when="1887-08-20">Aug: 20 '87</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Nothing special to write&#8212;I suppose you have lately rec'd some papers from
                me&#8212;We appear to be thro' the long &#38; fierce spell of hot weather&#8212;have
                had it very agreeable now for nearly a fortnight&#8212;John Burroughs<ptr
                    target="n0129"/> has been here for a couple of days<ptr target="bms.00004_n2"
                />&#8212;he is well&#8212;nothing new in my literary affairs&#8212;H[erbert]
                    G[ilchrist]<ptr target="n0262"/> is here &#38; is painting leisurely&#8212;he is
                well&#8212;I hear frequently f'm Dr Bucke<ptr target="n0119"/> and Kennedy<ptr
                    target="n3039"/>&#8212;I drove out twelve miles &#38; back yesterday&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
